79
00:06:21,580 --> 00:06:22,680
It's fine, okay?

80
00:06:22,860 --> 00:06:24,420
I'm sure you don't have worries like me.

81
00:06:24,580 --> 00:06:25,440
Just forget it, alright?

82
00:06:25,440 --> 00:06:31,060
Oh, man. Life just seems to be so unfair.

83
00:06:34,500 --> 00:06:37,760
