94
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:07,000
Hi.

95
00:07:07,740 --> 00:07:08,180
See?

96
00:07:08,380 --> 00:07:09,160
You're a magnet.

97
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:10,440
Hi.

98
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:14,480
I'm Constantine, the president of the Supernatural Phenomenon

99
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:14,720
Club.

100
00:07:15,300 --> 00:07:15,980
How are you doing?

101
00:07:16,380 --> 00:07:16,940
Oh, boy.

102
00:07:17,300 --> 00:07:18,540
Someone let the weirdos out.

103
00:07:19,080 --> 00:07:19,980
Give me a break.

104
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:21,840
