175
00:13:16,040 --> 00:13:17,960
First, the closer you get to your target,

176
00:13:18,080 --> 00:13:20,180
obviously, the better accuracy you'll have.

177
00:13:20,760 --> 00:13:22,480
And, of course, you'll need to find a place

178
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:23,980
where you can get off a clear shot.

179
00:13:24,520 --> 00:13:27,800
