190
00:14:39,660 --> 00:14:41,160
Uh, oh, yeah.

191
00:14:42,720 --> 00:14:48,000
I don't know why, but Thursday seems to be the most popular day of the week for visitors.

192
00:14:48,460 --> 00:14:53,340
Like that old man with his two young companions over there. And you, too, of course.

193
00:14:54,440 --> 00:14:57,400
I suspect you like the solitude of this forest.

194
00:14:58,460 --> 00:15:02,160
Uh, I'm enjoying it. And yourself?

195
00:15:02,160 --> 00:15:03,420
