200
00:15:51,260 --> 00:15:52,480
Gosh, that is such a shame.

201
00:16:22,720 --> 00:16:25,160
Are you ready for a fabulous prize?

202
00:16:25,340 --> 00:16:28,100
It's time to find out who knows the answers.

203
00:16:28,600 --> 00:16:31,600
