204
00:16:31,940 --> 00:16:33,880
And he's going to have a chance to win

205
00:16:33,880 --> 00:16:36,240
a brand-new, fully-equipped RV.

206
00:16:36,880 --> 00:16:38,740
Whoa! My family's been dreaming

207
00:16:38,740 --> 00:16:40,620
about going camping in one for years.

208
00:16:40,880 --> 00:16:43,240
Well, you'll be able to take them camping

209
00:16:43,240 --> 00:16:44,920
every weekend in style.

210
00:16:45,340 --> 00:16:48,560
